The,Virtual,International,Authority,File,is,a,project,from,the,OCLC,Office,of,Research,which,brings,together,authority,data,on,accepted,forms,of,author,names,and,work,titles,from,different,authority,files,in,libraries,worldwide,The,web,service,provides,a,way,to,search,and,retrieve,authority,records,providing,authoritative,versions,of,author,names,subject,headings,and,resource,titles,in,a,variety,of,formats